=Description=

"The UrbanA Wiki Database documents 33 approaches to tackling urban injustice and unsustainability, ranging from democratic governance and financial mechanisms to community gardens and Transition Towns.

The database is a living knowledge commons that serves as a resource from which city makers can take action. It is the fruit thus far of UrbanA’s collaborative journey that began in January 2019."
(https://medium.com/urban-arenas-for-sustainable-and-just-cities/33-ways-to-make-cities-just-sustainable-a47cfb19bc4f)

